                    },
                    "body": "Thank you for advice and responces, Emil Ivanov  and Basil Guevarra .\n\nBuy the way I hear ZF Dev Team members works on this matter.\nI will wait their to expect good results. :-) ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=yoshida@zend.co.jp",
                        "name": "yoshida@zend.co.jp",
