                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=evalder",
                        "name": "evalder",
                        "displayName": "EV",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Sorry, there was a bug in my method - empty input would return true, as is_readable would only check against the directories in include_path.\nAdding the following line to the beginning of the method fixes the problem.\n\t\tif ($filename === null || $filename === false || $filename === '' || !is_scalar($filename)) return false;\n\nThis change will not effect performance (noticeably anyway).",
